{"tid":346000,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"真正既長大係有唔開心可以自己解決","createTime":"2017-08-03T14:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T18:08:49.000Z","uid":101935,"like":179,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f293204d5584d8f90b1cdc6470e1decc9584b0b","tid":346000,"uid":101935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T14:31:18.000Z","msg":"或者有好多人都係成日自己面對<br />\n但總有啲人係要揾人傾訴先會睇得開<br />\n而真正既長大係你識得接受唔開心識得處理你嘅情緒唔會發放負能量<br />\n係時候要長大唔再打擾身邊人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca9b2ee6ea573700f3b9ebd4eb1225e8a418d4e","tid":346000,"uid":3273,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T14:32:04.000Z","msg":"燥鳩人底既都係垃圾"},{"pid":"ab0345bf20e95afbbcd8ee56223a6ea8be1e0b39","tid":346000,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":39,"score":-37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T14:34:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cba0696f68f2010eb5e028916c40c8856325cbea","tid":346000,"uid":23170,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T14:35:35.000Z","msg":"搵人傾下都係健康嘅抒發黎嘅，我覺得。前提係唔係由朝到晚都煩鳩住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cffeb9b6d4e96f28f87e775775dae9b8673de5f","tid":346000,"uid":133250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T14:37:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"319587b4acf17928bd4f5ef103bd4a1cfaa6e125","tid":346000,"uid":80788,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T14:43:51.000Z","msg":"唔知點解睇完你段野好sad <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其是望到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依個公仔<br />\n就算佢個樣笑得幾開心都feel到佢背後流緊眼淚咁<br />\n媽媽呀可唔可以唔大呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177c11f8f23929ef9d0c3e98c7d8c718b281a06b","tid":346000,"uid":101935,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T14:44:26.000Z","msg":"只有自己先能夠最明白自己"},{"pid":"c92a61128f3366b59f1437c726554a9c457cb8d2","tid":346000,"uid":101935,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T14:46:21.000Z","msg":"冇人能夠永遠陪伴你 而每日面對太多唔同挑戰 你亦冇可能每日搵人傾訴 點都係要靠自己撐住自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c69075634a611e950542e7ef41b0abccaec54d2","tid":346000,"uid":101935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T14:47:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知點解睇完你段野好sad <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其是望到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依個公仔<br />\n就算佢個樣笑得幾開心都feel到佢背後流緊眼淚咁<br />\n媽媽呀可唔可以唔大呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一日未有能力控制自己情緒一日都唔可以話自己長大了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c84332be3c88d83a9b4a7d24998d93f3aa0d6a0b","tid":346000,"uid":104006,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T17:26:44.000Z","msg":"睇到段野喊出泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近感悟好深 都係覺得人大咗好多野要自己解決<br />\n開心唔開心都要自己承擔 <br />\n甚至仲要分擔其他人嘅負能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加油啦大家"},{"pid":"c3afc5fcf59da6e91ad60803354dbb02d75b1786","tid":346000,"uid":58161,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T17:34:17.000Z","msg":"唔會發放負能量 永遠都係自己忍 <br />\n但唔識得處理情緒 所以一down既時候 就咩人都唔想接觸 直頭係想放自己入個箱入面 閂埋蓋既感覺"},{"pid":"d337f8163d06c791fade48b97e82287de2069bda","tid":346000,"uid":35106,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T17:38:24.000Z","msg":"同過人地講心事,不過對方一係講幾句反駁我既說話<br />\n一係就唔記得我講過<br />\n所以做人都係唔好咁認真<br />\n人人都有自己面對煩惱既,邊會有人肯錫住你花時間聽晒你講野又明白你呢<br />\n除左自己鐘意果個(直提係鐘意自己)或者父母(又係真係鐘意自己)<br />\n唔好將自己睇得咁重要,亦都唔好信晒人地果一刻對你既&quot;熱誠&quot;<br />\n我係咁同自己講"},{"pid":"65e01197ead470fae45a0f22a3661ab3d34737b0","tid":346000,"uid":85128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T19:08:14.000Z","msg":"啲道理我知架但真係做就做唔到<br />\n幾時先學識自己解決唔開心<br />\n唔想再煩到人<br />\n點解成日都咁易信人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b10e165480802f832ea3a1ff159517c698dfe3","tid":346000,"uid":101935,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T02:11:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇到段野喊出泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近感悟好深 都係覺得人大咗好多野要自己解決<br />\n開心唔開心都要自己承擔 <br />\n甚至仲要分擔其他人嘅負能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加油啦大家</blockquote><br />\n就算點樣揾人傾 最後都係要靠自己諗通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fbad011d2f92033914361ffab6f388e3dab8a29","tid":346000,"uid":101935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T02:12:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔會發放負能量 永遠都係自己忍 <br />\n但唔識得處理情緒 所以一down既時候 就咩人都唔想接觸 直頭係想放自己入個箱入面 閂埋蓋既感覺</blockquote><br />\n我都係咁 努力緊 唔想再煩任何人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9e25ce64fde004abb55871d0d34a1bed7525171","tid":346000,"uid":101935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T02:13:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同過人地講心事,不過對方一係講幾句反駁我既說話<br />\n一係就唔記得我講過<br />\n所以做人都係唔好咁認真<br />\n人人都有自己面對煩惱既,邊會有人肯錫住你花時間聽晒你講野又明白你呢<br />\n除左自己鐘意果個(直提係鐘意自己)或者父母(又係真係鐘意自己)<br />\n唔好將自己睇得咁重要,亦都唔好信晒人地果一刻對你既&quot;熱誠&quot;<br />\n我係咁同自己講</blockquote><br />\n我相信有人會花時間聽<br />\n只係到頭來都係要自己去解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb46d417e3e7ec064766610f00b93af8f4b95e8f","tid":346000,"uid":101935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T02:14:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲道理我知架但真係做就做唔到<br />\n幾時先學識自己解決唔開心<br />\n唔想再煩到人<br />\n點解成日都咁易信人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n解決解唔到就睇開啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df30ee720a5c2692485fd835b7a85ffdfcd1385","tid":346000,"uid":15070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T05:36:48.000Z","msg":"屌好中 呢排日日都有呢個覺悟 根本冇人係靠得住嘅因爲人性自私 只有自己先可以幫到自己 要學識唔去依賴人 唔對人地抱有仼何幻想 咁先唔會唔開心"},{"pid":"f0748991683603ca2387c425a4ddeab76033a569","tid":346000,"uid":15070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T05:41:02.000Z","msg":"呢個post啲comment好可怕係咪我啲分身黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢排真係俾呢樣嘢困擾得好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為唔開心 再諗到冇人可以同我分擔 冇人會願意同我分擔 就更加唔開心 孤獨感真係好強 身邊幾多人都好 條路都係得自己一個人行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93734e6023df6e0c33a04b6b2725c597f758829","tid":346000,"uid":101935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:16:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌好中 呢排日日都有呢個覺悟 根本冇人係靠得住嘅因爲人性自私 只有自己先可以幫到自己 要學識唔去依賴人 唔對人地抱有仼何幻想 咁先唔會唔開心</blockquote><br />\n唔係話唔可以有幻想，而係人永遠會幻想到最好，一有咩差池就會唔開心"},{"pid":"5a0d9e85ea77319fca15c48aa447f42662d22f45","tid":346000,"uid":101935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:18:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個post啲comment好可怕係咪我啲分身黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢排真係俾呢樣嘢困擾得好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為唔開心 再諗到冇人可以同我分擔 冇人會願意同我分擔 就更加唔開心 孤獨感真係好強 身邊幾多人都好 條路都係得自己一個人行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都會咁諗，有時怕自己太煩唔想周圍散負能量，但偏偏靠自己又搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d5c7cbec158c8fd7fc8e4cbe1351055d416c91","tid":346000,"uid":14230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:19:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f68a322516d32b55f173543fa1e0b07d2de0517b","tid":346000,"uid":101935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:45:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收嗲