ces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗咁多 咁敏感<br />\n點解唔可以諗嘢簡單啲 做人開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁嘅性格仲怪人唔關心你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我其實收埋得好好 冇人知我好辛苦 連春唔俾自己嗌 因為嗌咗都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又一個循環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同你差不多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 極度神經質 我呢段時間都知自己性格有問題想改變下 萬事起頭難 呢段日子情緒好不穩 但好快就適應 加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3314cba30ce7931c777624cf6dd88e0537301a2d","tid":346000,"uid":25044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T08:51:12.000Z","msg":"解決唔到仲未可以自己處理到<br />\n但係唔想同任何人商量點算"},{"pid":"f4e4ef62911f42f126d884cc98ce4661f43a1c8f","tid":346000,"uid":101935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T09:37:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>解決唔到仲未可以自己處理到<br />\n但係唔想同任何人商量點算</blockquote><br />\n遺忘"},{"pid":"1f4d5b67c5f8d2d9201906c384d8810505b02de3","tid":346000,"uid":124403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T12:49:00.000Z","msg":"咁解決唔到又可以點呀，on lun 9"},{"pid":"7036ec68f906efec29fa94731374d383e1ca8e5d","tid":346000,"uid":31733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T12:55:29.000Z","msg":"其實只係變左將負面情緒收埋收埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06371323dc599717d9585367448b8fe4247f7415","tid":346000,"uid":101935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:50:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁解決唔到又可以點呀，on lun 9</blockquote><br />\n我得就唔洗上來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938dc0502940e4a342ebefa02a2d214051fb074c","tid":346000,"uid":122211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:51:31.000Z","msg":"